uage>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>By car: from the airport follow the direction of Palma. Once on the motorway, take the first exit on the right ("Coll d'en Rabassa", approx. 1 km). Go over the crossroads and turn left in the direction of "Son Ferriol". After a few metres you will meet another junction. Turn right onto the motorway to Manacor. After 50 km follow the directions to "S'Illot, Porto-Cristo". By public transport: from the airport take the bus to Palma. It travels as far as the "Plaza de Espa√±a". Here you will find the station and bus stop. If you wish to take the train, take the train to "Manacor and S'Illot". From Palma you can take the "Palma-S'Illot" bus from various bus stops. The bus will stop at the hotel's entrance. You will then need to cross the bridge over the beach to reach reception. Taxis are also available.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Guests are able to use the Thalasso health and spa area of the neighbouring hotel which lies around 150 m away. Guests receive a special 50 % discount from the normal price.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>The hotel comprises a total of 99 rooms set over four floors. Facilities on offer include a welcoming foyer with 24-hour reception, a hotel safe, a currency exchange counter, a cloakroom, and a panorama lift. A pleasant bar with terrace and a restaurant cater to guests' culinary wishes. In addition, the hotel features a TV room with satellite TV, games machines, and an Internet terminal (for an added fee). A laundry service for shirts, dresses etc is also provided along with medical assistance (fees apply).</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>TVInRoom</Code><Text>TV in room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MoneyExchange</Code><Text>Money